---
title: Directory
description: The BUKMARK.CLUB directory.
layout: base.njk
permalink: /directory/index.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<h1>Directory</h1>
<p>
  This is our directory of {{ info.directorySize }} websites that provide a curated collection of bookmarks and/or links to other websites.
</p>
{% include "directoryInfo.njk" %}
<details class="mb1">
  <summary>
    <b>Disclaimer</b>
  </summary>
  <ul style="list-style-type: square; padding-left: 2rem;">
    <li class="mb1">
      We do <i>not</i> accept any responsibility for any linked site's content.
    </li>
    <li class="mb1">
      We try to take good care of this directory, but this is the internet - any listed website can change at any moment. Please <a href="https://github.com/ttntm/bukmark.club/issues" rel="noopener" target="_blank">[file an issue]</a> or <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=The_Issue">[email us]</a> if you should find broken links or discover any other issues with a site listed below.
    </li>
    <li>
      If your site appears in this directory and you're unhappy with the listing or its inclusion, please <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=Update or Removal of Site:">[let us know]</a>.
    </li>
  </ul>
</details>
<h2>Index</h2>
<ul class="flex flex-wrap gap1 mb2">
  {% for letter, letterPages in collections.directory %}
    <li>
      <a href="#section-{{ letter }}">[{{ letter }}]</a>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
{% for letter, letterPages in collections.directory %}
  <article class="{% if not loop.last %}mb2{% endif %}">
    <div class="flex align-items-center justify-content-between" style="border-bottom: 1px solid slateblue;">
      <h2 id="section-{{ letter }}" class="m0" style="border: 0;">[{{ letter }}]</h2>
      <a class="block" href="#top" title="Back to top">[^]</a>
    </div>
    <ul class="grid grid3 gap2 my1">
      {% for page in letterPages %}
        {% include "card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </article>
{% endfor %}
